1
00:00:48,310 --> 00:00:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Earthquake!</font>

2
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

3
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mine's collapsing!</font>

4
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

5
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's collapsing!</font>

6
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run! It's collapsing!</font>

7
00:01:10,350 --> 00:01:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run! It's collapsing!</font>

8
00:01:12,430 --> 00:01:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

9
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Witch!</font>

10
00:01:59,450 --> 00:02:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a witch!</font>

11
00:02:25,850 --> 00:02:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die, you filthy witch!</font>

12
00:02:28,990 --> 00:02:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die!</font>

13
00:02:31,410 --> 00:02:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's just a young girl.</font>

14
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would've thought...</font>

15
00:02:37,050 --> 00:02:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Burn her to death!</font>

16
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn the witch!</font>

17
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness is truly busy!</font>

18
00:02:47,420 --> 00:02:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He doesn't even have time 
to render a verdict.</font>

19
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter, do you think</font>

20
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness will get out of bed this time?</font>

21
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, our Border Town is remote 
and sparsely populated,</font>

22
00:03:04,170 --> 00:03:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and with a witch causing trouble,</font>

23
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness probably 
doesn't want to stay long.</font>

24
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should hurry back to Graycastle.</font>

25
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tyre.</font>

26
00:03:24,230 --> 00:03:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Barov.</font>

27
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is His Highness?</font>

28
00:03:28,010 --> 00:03:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness... is still asleep.</font>

29
00:03:32,830 --> 00:03:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

30
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

31
00:03:35,770 --> 00:03:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Your Highness.</font>

32
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, it's time.</font>

33
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

34
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

35
00:04:03,690 --> 00:04:06,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, wake up! Wake up!</font>

36
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

37
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

38
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where am I—</font>

39
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for the witch's execution.</font>

40
00:04:17,290 --> 00:04:20,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone is waiting for your verdict.</font>

41
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Verdict?</i></font>

42
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What verdict?</i></font>

43
00:04:27,170 --> 00:04:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I dreaming?</i></font>

44
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

45
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This... This feels so real!</i></font>

46
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

47
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

48
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

49
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

50
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

51
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov.</font>

52
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your name is Barov.</font>

53
00:04:57,370 --> 00:04:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

54
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it's me, your servant Barov.</font>

55
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, it's time for the execution.</font>

56
00:05:06,670 --> 00:05:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go out.</font>

57
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's observe the situation for now.</i></font>

58
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, what's wrong?</font>

59
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, let's go now.</font>

60
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What on earth have I been through?</i></font>

61
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness the Prince is coming out!</font>

62
00:06:11,650 --> 00:06:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince!</font>

63
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence!</font>

64
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang her! Hang her!</font>

65
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>W-Witch?</i></font>

66
00:06:40,180 --> 00:06:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, please give your verdict quickly.</font>

67
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:46,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she... the witch you're talking about?</font>

68
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

69
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Witch hunts...</i></font>

70
00:06:51,020 --> 00:06:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No... this is too absurd.</i></font>

71
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm tired. Postpone the verdict. 
Everyone is dismissed for today.</font>

72
00:06:58,950 --> 00:06:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

73
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, this is not a joke.</font>

74
00:07:01,970 --> 00:07:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once a witch is identified, 
she should be executed immediately.</font>

75
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otherwise, it will attract other witches.</font>

76
00:07:06,990 --> 00:07:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter... Lannis.</font>

77
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

78
00:07:13,890 --> 00:07:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My... Chief Knight.</font>

79
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

80
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not afraid, right?</font>

81
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it better for a few more witches 
to come so we can catch them all at once?</font>

82
00:07:24,730 --> 00:07:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

83
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, why not hang the witch?</font>

84
00:10:08,190 --> 00:10:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An unreliable prince.</i></font>

85
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An insignificant territory.</i></font>

86
00:10:13,370 --> 00:10:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An uncivilized society.</i></font>

87
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A dark and ignorant era.</i></font>

88
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A sudden battle for the throne.</i></font>

89
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What can I possibly do... 
in this chaotic world?</i></font>

90
00:10:54,730 --> 00:10:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since I'm here, I'll make the best of it.</i></font>

91
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From this day on,</i></font>

92
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I am Roland Wimbledon.</i></font>

93
00:11:13,780 --> 00:11:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Your Highness.</font>

94
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, you summoned me?</font>

95
00:11:19,890 --> 00:11:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov, have a seat.</font>

96
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

97
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, why didn't you 
order the execution yesterday?</font>

98
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This matter is of grave importance. 
It cannot be delayed.</font>

99
00:11:39,070 --> 00:11:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Why is that?</font>

100
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:45,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guards reported sightings of 
suspected witches in the western forest.</font>

101
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They found this there.</font>

102
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Insignia of the
Sacred Mountain and Magic Eye.</font>

103
00:11:51,090 --> 00:11:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the emblem of the 
Witch Cooperation Association.</font>

104
00:11:54,010 --> 00:11:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Witch Cooperation Association? 
What's that?</font>

105
00:11:57,110 --> 00:11:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An organization of witches.</font>

106
00:11:58,850 --> 00:12:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before it was formed, witches acted alone.</font>

107
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the Association is different.</font>

108
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wants to unite all witches</font>

109
00:12:05,990 --> 00:12:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to search for the so-called Holy Mountain.</font>

110
00:12:09,300 --> 00:12:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said... the Holy Mountain?</font>

111
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rumor has it that they can only find eternal 
peace by going to the Holy Mountain.</font>

112
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For this purpose, the Association even 
actively lures others into becoming witches.</font>

113
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't a group of baby girls go missing 
from the Port of Clearwater last year?</font>

114
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rumor has it that they were behind it.</font>

115
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're afraid the Association will hear 
she didn't die, and come to rescue her.</font>

116
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precisely, Your Highness.</font>

117
00:12:32,450 --> 00:12:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those lunatics would even steal babies.</font>

118
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:37,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They probably wouldn't 
abandon a fallen comrade.</font>

119
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, you must 
execute that witch quickly.</font>

120
00:12:40,430 --> 00:12:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be a problem if she 
attracted her companions.</font>

121
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once someone becomes a witch, 
she gains terrifying power.</font>

122
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even knights would struggle to match her.</font>

123
00:12:50,250 --> 00:12:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mentioned power.</font>

124
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of power?</font>

125
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how did you catch her?</font>

126
00:12:55,650 --> 00:12:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few days ago, 
the North Slope Mine collapsed.</font>

127
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She used witchcraft and exposed her identity.</font>

128
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of witchcraft?</font>

129
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She unleashed hellfire</font>

130
00:13:06,260 --> 00:13:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and burnt a man to death.</font>

131
00:13:07,940 --> 00:13:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The victim melted like wax,</font>

132
00:13:10,310 --> 00:13:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with his head and most of his 
body all over the ground.</font>

133
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't want to see something like that.</font>

134
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Your Highness, let's deal with 
that witch as soon as possible.</font>

135
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take me to see her.</font>

136
00:13:23,300 --> 00:13:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

137
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to see the witch?</font>

138
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

139
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

140
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

141
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, wait, Your Highness.</font>

142
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why death by hanging?</font>

143
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't burning at the stake the 
usual way of executing witches?</font>

144
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

145
00:13:47,900 --> 00:13:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she's not afraid of fire.</font>

146
00:13:52,810 --> 00:13:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, this is far too dangerous.</font>

147
00:13:55,060 --> 00:13:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're dealing with an evil witch.</font>

148
00:13:57,160 --> 00:14:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though she's bound by God's Locket of 
Retribution, we can't guarantee it's safe.</font>

149
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can't face evil, 
then how can you defeat it?</font>

150
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought my Chief Knight 
understood this principle.</font>

151
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must act within your capabilities.</font>

152
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Recklessness is not bravery.</font>

153
00:14:10,110 --> 00:14:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're saying we should uphold 
justice against weaker foes,</font>

154
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:15,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but ignore stronger ones?</font>

155
00:14:16,410 --> 00:14:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Your Highness. That's not what I meant.</font>

156
00:15:26,530 --> 00:15:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax, Carter. Stand down.</font>

157
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, Your Highness...</font>

158
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name?</font>

159
00:15:33,570 --> 00:15:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the Lord of Border Town,</font>

160
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Fourth Prince of the Kingdom 
of Graycastle, Roland Wimbledon.</font>

161
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name?</font>

162
00:15:41,090 --> 00:15:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Anna.</font>

163
00:15:43,590 --> 00:15:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna, what happened 
in the mine that day?</font>

164
00:15:46,310 --> 00:15:48,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to tell me in detail.</font>

165
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father is a miner.</font>

166
00:15:56,710 --> 00:15:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the mine collapsed, 
he was working inside.</font>

167
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ran into the mine to find him.</font>

168
00:16:03,570 --> 00:16:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of the collapse,</font>

169
00:16:04,980 --> 00:16:07,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my father's leg was trapped 
under the fallen rocks.</font>

170
00:16:08,580 --> 00:16:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Another miner who escaped with him</font>

171
00:16:10,940 --> 00:16:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">tried to steal the few coins he had on him.</font>

172
00:16:15,070 --> 00:16:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those were my father's life savings,</font>

173
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:21,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">our entire livelihood.</font>

174
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So my father fought back 
with all his strength.</font>

175
00:16:27,350 --> 00:16:28,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I found them,</font>

176
00:16:28,850 --> 00:16:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw the miner with his pickaxe raised, 
about to kill my father.</font>

177
00:16:34,410 --> 00:16:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I... killed him.</font>

178
00:16:43,570 --> 00:16:45,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how were you captured?</font>

179
00:16:46,300 --> 00:16:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone... reported me.</font>

180
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reported? Who reported you?</font>

181
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was her father, Your Highness.</font>

182
00:16:58,420 --> 00:16:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

183
00:16:59,740 --> 00:17:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it was her father who reported her?</font>

184
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably for the bounty.</font>

185
00:17:07,770 --> 00:17:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those who discover and report witches</font>

186
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:12,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">receive a reward of 25 gold royals.</font>

187
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For someone with a broken leg,</font>

188
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that's enough to secure the rest of his life.</font>

189
00:17:21,580 --> 00:17:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was a grown man.</font>

190
00:17:23,910 --> 00:17:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you kill him?</font>

191
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was what you call...</font>

192
00:17:30,530 --> 00:17:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the power of the devil.</font>

193
00:17:32,650 --> 00:17:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? The power of the devil.</font>

194
00:17:34,730 --> 00:17:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you show me?</font>

195
00:17:37,010 --> 00:17:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

196
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, she's currently being 
suppressed by God's Stone of Retaliation.</font>

197
00:17:41,490 --> 00:17:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she's released, the consequences 
will be unimaginable.</font>

198
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this your first time 
meeting a witch, Lord?</font>

199
00:17:47,870 --> 00:17:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your curiosity might kill you.</font>

200
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you truly are an evil devil, 
then it shouldn't be me who dies.</font>

201
00:17:54,800 --> 00:17:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should be your father.</font>

202
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:10,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness. Your Highness!</font>

203
00:18:10,490 --> 00:18:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, what are you doing?</font>

204
00:18:13,230 --> 00:18:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

205
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, what are you doing?</font>

206
00:18:21,190 --> 00:18:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on.</font>

207
00:18:22,770 --> 00:18:24,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really a pitiful girl,</font>

208
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or are you a devil with 
superb acting skills?</font>

209
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:29,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see.</font>

210
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

211
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, let's get out of here!</font>

212
00:18:57,540 --> 00:18:58,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Carter!</font>

213
00:18:58,730 --> 00:19:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, look!</font>

214
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's there to see?</font>

215
00:19:02,290 --> 00:19:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The flames...</font>

216
00:19:03,810 --> 00:19:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The flames aren't coming out.</font>

217
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's consciously controlling the flames.</font>

218
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's not going to hurt us.</font>

219
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

220
00:19:18,860 --> 00:19:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

221
00:19:55,810 --> 00:19:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord, has your curiosity been satisfied?</font>

222
00:20:00,540 --> 00:20:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you kill me now?</font>

223
00:20:22,390 --> 00:20:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Miss Anna.</font>

224
00:20:25,890 --> 00:20:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to hire you.</font>

